# ============================================================================
# COMMENTS
# ============================================================================

# Lines starting with '#' are comments
# Use '/' to specify directories
# Use '*' for wildcards
# Use '!' to negate (do NOT ignore)
# Example: !important.txt (will NOT ignore important.txt even if *.txt is ignored)

